2006-12-29 Jorge Gascón  <jgascon@gsyc.escet.urjc.es>

    * pyMLS/data_manager.py:
      Changed multi-query implementation to one query per cursor.execute().
          Changed query commits to connection.commit()
    * pyMLS/parser.py: Parser class now purifies processed text (converts every
          processed character to ASCII code).
    * pyMLS/dump_db_transformer.py: Now this transformer uses announce method
          using observer pattern characteristics.
    * pyMLS/mls_structures.py: Parser class now purifies input text at
           __init__method (converts every input character to ASCII code).
    * pyMLS/utils.py: More effective purify_text method.
    * pyMLS/message_parser.py: Now this class can process Brazilian emails.
    * pyMLS/main_subsystem.py: More intuitive project directories hierarchy.
    * pyMLS/basic_transformer.py: Now this transformer uses announce method
          using observer pattern characteristics.
    * pyMLS/stats_subsystem.py: Nows this class does one analysis per project,
          nor per mailing_list.
    * pyMLS/config_parser.py: Some unuseful tags removed.
    * pyMLS/seal_xml_transformer.py: Now this transformer uses announce method
          using observer pattern characteristics.


